    public interface StringConverter<Value>
extends Converter<java.lang.String,​Value>
    A bi-directional converter between String values and values of the given type. The Converter interface converts from String to type <Value> and the method toString(Object) converts a <Value> back to a String.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    BaseStringConverter
